---
title: Harissa Beef Meatballs & Garlic Yoghurt with Roast Veggie Couscous & Almonds
description: Explore a fusion like no other – beef meatballs cooked in an aromatic harissa paste. When they come together with a fluffy
couscous, tossed through with roasted veggies like carrot and cauliflower and cooled off with a hit of garlic yoghurt you’ll be
pleasantly surprised how the flavours meld together in the most exquisite way.
